ft: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em;&quot;&gt;&lt;a-img alt=&quot;&quot; height=&quot;2368&quot; high-dpi-quality=&quot;70&quot; layout=&quot;responsive&quot; quality=&quot;85&quot; src=&quot;https://news.google.com/imgs/18/3/0/1/3/2/3/8/Foto3-336e86268939b7c8.jpg&quot; width=&quot;3692&quot;&gt;&lt;/a-img&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;figcaption class=&quot;a-caption &quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em;&quot;&gt;Fred Board Assembly concluded 2nd Sunday in Advent&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;											', '1607104980_1.jpeg', 1, '2020-12-04 10:03:57', '2020-12-04 10:03:57');
INSERT INTO `post_list` (`id`, `title`, `category_id`, `content`, `cover_img`, `status`, `date_published`, `date_created`) VALUES
(4, 'The biggest demand is causing online stores to collapse', 3, '&lt;p style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(65, 65, 65); font-family: Roboto, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;If you want to catch the new PlayStation 5 before Christmas, you need perseverance and luck. It is true that new allocations of the console are always released for sale. But demand is greater than supply.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(65, 65, 65); font-family: Roboto, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;PlayStation available in Germany from November 19 (&lt;span class=&quot;TshowLinkInXML&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.t-online.de/digital/id_88958444/playstation-5-im-test-diesen-innovationsvorteil-hat-die-neue-sony-konsole.html&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(206, 24, 30);&quot;&gt;Read our test of the console here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;) &ndash; At least in theory. As expected, the new console was resold shortly after it went on sale. As Christmas gets closer and closer fans and distributors alike will have to wait again and again.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(65, 65, 65); font-family: Roboto, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;A small group was last released for sale on Thursday, December 3rd. On that day, fans can try their luck at things like Otto, GameStop, Amazon, Euronics, Expert and Medimax. However, due to the heavy load the online stores of the dealers are often not available. Anyone who is able to place an order successfully still needs to be patient &ndash; dealers will sometimes give very different delivery times.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(65, 65, 65); font-family: Roboto, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Hopefully the new game console will arrive before Christmas. But what are the chances for those who have missed all the order rounds so far? We will keep you updated with this article when the PS5 comes back to stores. Our questions also provide additional tips for purchasing.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 22px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-weight: 700; font-family: Roboto, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.35;&quot;&gt;&lt;a target=&quot;_blank&quot; class=&quot;ara&quot; name=&quot;a0&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(206, 24, 30);&quot;&gt;Can I buy a PlayStation 5 at the store?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(65, 65, 65); font-family: Roboto, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;No. Currently, consoles are only sold through online stores. Disappointed buyers can save themselves a trip to the store: if there are no more PlayStations to buy online, the console is simply sold out, you have to trust the next round of supplies.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(65, 65, 65); font-family: Roboto, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;This strategy, which is definitely disgusting to fans, is aimed at preventing long lines and clutter in stores. Scenes like that since launch&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.t-online.de/themen/ps4&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(206, 24, 30);&quot;&gt;PlayStation 4&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;Keep in mind that corona infections cannot be justified.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;margin: 0em 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(65, 65, 65); font-family: Roboto, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; clear: both;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.haveeru.com.mv/winners-and-losers-of-new-sec-soccer-program-2020/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; class=&quot;u2f02a5eb425a973096b03649e968aec7&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(206, 24, 30); width: 796px; display: block; font-weight: 700; opacity: 1; transition: opacity 250ms ease 0s; padding-top: 1em !important; padding-bottom: 1em !important; border: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ctaText&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: inherit;&quot;&gt;READ&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;postTitle&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: inherit; text-decoration-line: underline !important;&quot;&gt;Winners and losers of new SEC soccer program 2020&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(65, 65, 65); font-family: Roboto, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;But what works: Order a console online and pick it up at the store. Mediamark, Saturn and Gamestop provide this service.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 22px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-weight: 700; font-family: Roboto, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.35;&quot;&gt;&lt;a target=&quot;_blank&quot; class=&quot;ara&quot; name=&quot;a0&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(206, 24, 30);&quot;&gt;Where can I buy a PlayStation 5?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(65, 65, 65); font-family: Roboto, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The following vendors sell Sony consoles in German-speaking countries:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 22px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-weight: 700; font-family: Roboto, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.35;&quot;&gt;&lt;a target=&quot;_blank&quot; class=&quot;ara&quot; name=&quot;a0&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(206, 24, 30);&quot;&gt;What should I look for when purchasing?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(65, 65, 65); font-family: Roboto, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Even after a successful order is placed, the console should never come up. Even at the pre-order stage, many retailers were forced to cancel subsequent orders. This was due to a combination of technical issues, poor planning and distribution issues. Like many electronics manufacturers, Sony suffers from manufacturing problems&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.t-online.de/themen/corona-krise&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(206, 24, 30);&quot;&gt;Corona-Chris&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(65, 65, 65); font-family: Roboto, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Also make sure that users are ordering only from trusted stores. There is a fear that countless fake stores will try to intercept frustrated fans as there is high demand.&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;TshowLinkInXML&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.t-online.de/digital/sicherheit/id_85814800/fake-shops-erkennen-diese-sieben-anzeichen-lassen-den-betrug-auffliegen.html&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(206, 24, 30);&quot;&gt;Here&rsquo;s how to spot attempted scams like this&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 22px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-weight: 700; font-family: Roboto, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.35;&quot;&gt;&lt;a target=&quot;_blank&quot; class=&quot;ara&quot; name=&quot;a0&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(206, 24, 30);&quot;&gt;What is the price of the PlayStation 5?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(65, 65, 65); font-family: Roboto, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The PlayStation 5 is available in two versions: the standard model costs 500 euros. The driverless version &ndash; also known as the &ldquo;digital version&rdquo; &ndash; is available for 400 euros. Some distributors charge a reduced VAT rate of 16 percent.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(65, 65, 65); font-family: Roboto, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Except for the driver, the consoles are technically identical. Users do not have to compromise on performance when buying a cheaper model.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 22px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-weight: 700; font-family: Roboto, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.35;&quot;&gt;Resellers charge higher prices on eBay&lt;/h3&gt;