e&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The second dual sensor controller costs 70 euros. This is required to run PS5 headlines. If you only want to use PS4 games, you can continue to use your old gameplay.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(65, 65, 65); font-family: Roboto, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Remote controls and HD cameras are also available. Headsets and charging stations are currently sold out. Parts will be shipped to the console a week in advance, starting November 12th. You can also buy some of them in stores.&lt;/p&gt;											', '1607105100_2.jpg', 1, '2020-12-04 10:05:08', '2020-12-04 10:05:08'),
(5, 'Material costs about $ 400', 3, '						&lt;p style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(65, 65, 65); font-family: Roboto, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;time datetime=&quot;2020-12-03T14:41:00+01:00&quot; class=&quot;cxenseignore&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;December 3, 2020 at 2:41 pm&lt;/time&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;authorName cxenseignore&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;From&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;editorNameLink noAuthorImg&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;Klaus Ludwig&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&ndash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;According to the Japanese business newspaper Nikkei, the material cost for the iPhone 12 should be around $ 400. The OLED display and 5G modem are the most expensive components.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;articleTextBody&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(65, 65, 65); font-family: Roboto, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;textContainer&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em;&quot;&gt;New smartphones launch from Apple&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.apple.com/de/shop/buy-iphone/iphone-12&quot; title=&quot;rund 780 Euro f&uuml;r das iPhone 12 Mini&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(206, 24, 30);&quot;&gt;780 euros for the iPhone 12 min&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;With a 5.4-inch display and 64 gigabytes of non-expandable memory. The big iPhone 12 costs at least 880 euros. Both Pro models of the iPhone 12 cost at least 1,000 euros. Japanese business magazine Nikkei now estimates material costs based on a tear. Components of the iPhone 12 are said to cost 3,373 for the iPhone 12 Pro&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://asia.nikkei.com/Business/Technology/iPhone-12-teardown-showcases-South-Korean-parts-makers&quot; title=&quot;liegen die Kosten wohl bei 406 US-Dollar&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(206, 24, 30);&quot;&gt;The cost is probably 6 406&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;anchorHeadline&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0